<abstract><t>In some use cases, e.g.,Lightweight 4over6 (lw4o6) [RFC7596], the client may require not just one port, but a port set.  This document defines an extension to the Port Control Protocol (PCP) allowing clients to manipulate sets of ports as a whole.  This is accomplished by a new MAP option: PORT_SET.</t></abstract>

